article_title: Drive-by shooting damages north Wichita home
article_text:
A residence is damaged after a drive-by shooting with people inside the home just before midnight Saturday in north Wichita.

Two female victims told arriving Wichita police they were inside a home near Arkansas and 21st Street when they heard several gunshots outside. The women telling police they noticed new damage to the residence, but that they were not injured.

Police say there is no description of any suspects or possible suspect vehicles.
